earth and ashes ( persian : خاکستر و خاک ) is a 2004 afghan film directed by atiq rahimi . it was afghanistan 's submission to the 77th academy awards for the academy award for best foreign language film , but was not accepted as a nominee . it was also screened in the un certain regard section at the 2004 cannes film festival . it won the golden dhow award at the 2005 zanzibar international film festival .